 will complicate gazebo's linking with other dependencies.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The simbody developers have expressed some interest in <code>c++11</code> features (starting with <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://github.com/simbody/simbody/pull/123\" rel=\"nofollow\">this pull request</a> that simply fixes some build issues and adds a continuous integration build option for <code>c++11</code>.</p>\n<p>If simbody moves to require <code>c++11</code> support, it is my understanding that this will complicate gazebo's linking with other dependencies.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-02-17T18:32:02.275331+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:43:27.321289+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1050}